Class LanguageDetailsChecker

java.lang.Object

      sandra.libs.asr.asrmultilinguallib.LanguageDetailsChecker

public class LanguageDetailsChecker
extends android.content.BroadcastReceiver

receives the speech recognition language details from RecognizerIntent.ACTION_GET_LANGUAGE_DETAILS and then calls back to a OnLanguageDetailsListener
